My name is Jordan "Jay" Andrew Merkel. I am a student at George Mason University from Vienna, Virginia. I am studying Writing and Rhetoric in the English department. I plan to earn a BA in English with a minor in Spanish. After I graduate, I hope to publish my first fiction book series as a billingual audio drama.
